# Catch - 7916-TPG - 12065-PNB

This is a compatibility patch for:

- [TN's Class M (and Starborn Guardian) Ship Building (7916-TPG)](https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/7916) by [TheOGTennessee](https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/TheOGTennessee)
	- Permission to patch granted by:
		- [Nexus Mods - Mod Page - Permissions](https://web.archive.org/web/20241215232430/https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/7916)
	- Donate:

		[![PayPal Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/PayPal-white?style=flat&logo=paypal&logoColor=black)](https://www.paypal.com/donate?business=TheOGTennessee@gmail.com)
- [Captain's Choice - A Shipbuilding Overhaul (12065-PNB)](https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/12065) by [RbtRvltin](https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/RbtRvltin)
	- Permission to patch granted by:
		- [Nexus Mods - Mod Page - Permissions](https://web.archive.org/web/20241215232626/https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/12065)

Both make changes to the same ship thrusters. This compatibility patch merges these so you get the best of both worlds.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This compatibility patch is an independent creation and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or officially supported by the original author(s) of the mods involved.

Find more compatibility patches here: [Catch Collection](https://github.com/catch-group/catch-collection)

## Recommended Load Order

1. TN's Class M (and Starborn Guardian) Ship Building
2. Captain's Choice - A Shipbuilding Overhaul
3. Catch - 7916-TPG - 12065-PNB
